# Async Patterns

## Event Loop
- Use `async def` for I/O (STT, TTS, LLM, audio); avoid blocking the event loop
- Don't call `time.sleep()`; use `await asyncio.sleep()`
- CPU-bound work (Whisper inference) may block; consider `run_in_executor` if needed

## Retries
- Use `retry_async()` for transient errors (OSError, TimeoutError, ConnectionError)
- Exponential backoff: 1s → 2s → 4s; configurable via `base_delay`, `max_attempts`
- Don't retry non-transient errors (validation, auth failures)

## Streaming
- Prefer `AsyncIterator[str]` for LLM → TTS; buffer at sentence boundaries
- Cancel or interrupt cleanly; respect `interrupt()` on TTS engines
